    BlockFieldAnWrapper, FunctionFieldAnWrapper

    public abstract class BaseFieldAnWrapper<T>
extends CMLBaseField
    A CML field (block) wrapper class. It calls the block to perform transient simulation. The block type and parameters are set based its CML annotation
